Package: scoreMVAQ
Title: Score the Michigan Vision-related Anxiety Questionnaire
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Andrews", , "chrisaa@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5130-6374"))
Description: Package has one function, scoreMVAQ(), which takes a data.frame of responses provided by patients and returns domain scores (and standard errors) for the 2 MVAQ domains: Anxiety about Rod Function and Anxiety about Cone Function.
